channel.title: Help with adding models command [will REP]
channel.description:
I found this command was extremely helpful when adding models, i would of found it impossible to make my 317 HD without this command. So i am going to share it with you, full credits to Deltascape. Ok, open up your client.java client side. On edit, press find, or hit ctrl + f, and search this. Code: model There, you will probably see a command similar to this one.
I found this VERY VERY helpful guide http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,363483.0.html and my server doesn't have the add model command. So I opened client.java and trl+f and typed "model" just like it said to. But it takes me no where. What should I do?
